OL,3,CMan jailed after being found guilty of
OL,4,Colder brother's murder
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for life after
OL,7,Fhe was found guilty of the murder of
OL,8,Fhis older brother.
OL,10,FDarren Steel, 41, from Morriston,
OL,11,FSwansea, was found guilty of the
OL,12,Fmurder of his sibling, Martin Steel,
OL,13,Fon Thursday, South Wales Police said.
OL,15,FThe body of 48-year-old Martin Steel
OL,16,Fwas found at an address on Hill View
OL,17,FCrescent, Clase, shortly after 10:30am
OL,18,Fon 20 May 2023.
