OL,3,CMan jailed after being found guilty of
OL,4,Colder brother's murder
OL,6,FThe defendant was sentenced to life in
OL,7,Fprison with a minimum term of 20 years
OL,8,Fin respect of the murder conviction
OL,9,Fand counts of GBH and ABH from his
OL,10,Finitial trial, the force said.
OL,12,FDetective Inspector Stuart Prendiville
OL,13,Fsaid: "This has been a long and
OL,14,Fcomplex investigation into an incident
OL,15,Fwhich has shocked the communities of
OL,16,FClase, Morriston and the wider
OL,17,Fcommunity of Swansea. The impact on
OL,18,Fthe family has been significant.
