OL,3,CMan jailed after being found guilty of
OL,4,Colder brother's murder
OL,6,F"Darren Steel committed the ultimate
OL,7,Fbetrayal against his older brother and
OL,8,Fcaused further distress by pleading
OL,9,Fnot guilty and putting the family
OL,10,Fthrough the ordeal of not one, but two
OL,11,Ftrials.
OL,13,F"Darren Steel is a violent and
OL,14,Fdangerous individual and the life
OL,15,Fsentence and minimum tariff of 20
OL,16,Fyears is wholly justified in this case.
OL,18,F"We are relieved with the outcome and
OL,19,Fglad that the court proceedings have
OL,20,Fnow come to an end. Our thoughts are
OL,21,Fwith the family."
